  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and when we came from school, she was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we left to school, she was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She took care on all our needs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was very devoted mother to the children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She also, which was funny when I think about it-- that my brother and myself, many times, we would do certain things that normally we should not do.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like, for example, winter-- to take a bicycle and drive around the, the dining room around-- with the bicycle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, we knew that we shouldn't do it, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But when my mother told us many times to stop, we knew what is the limit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that when she said, I'm going to call your father-- and when we-- we still didn't stop until we knew that she's going to do it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then we would stop.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because we realized that she did not want to burden our father with unnecessary problems.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
